works.description: After Range Rover, Audi and MINI, we have Carroll Shelby from the automobile world with their offering on two wheels – the Shelby Cruiser. Carroll Shelby Licensing has teamed up with bike maker Felt Bicycles to design and develop a limited edition cruiser that “exudes the Shelby image and culture.” The bike flaunts the Wimbledon White and Guardsman Blue paint scheme that was seen on many of Shelby’s vintage cars. The bike boasts Felt’s hydro-formed aluminum tank frame, three-speed Shimano Nexus internal gearing and 36-spoke wheels.
